    {
      "id": "error-card-notes",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Error Card Notes",
      "position": {
        "x": 620,
        "y": 320
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Error Card\n\nThis graph defines the shared fallback node for visible graph failures.\n\n- `Port View` exposes the class artifact\n- `Icon View` provides semantic-zoom identity\n- `Node View` renders the actual error surface from structured error-message data\n- `Editor View` edits the canonical message fields\n\nIntended first-wave cases:\n- missing target\n- missing binding\n- unavailable payload\n- authority-reduced preview",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.error-card.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.error-card.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
